%^YELLOW%^Skill: Spellcraft

%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^A player's spellcraft skill indicates their knowledge of magic and its effects. It involves knowledge of spells, scrolls and magical items, and the use of these abilities and items.

%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Stat basis: %^WHITE%^intelligence
%^BOLD%^%^CYAN%^Current areas of influence: %^WHITE%^scroll use, spell recognition, identification of items, spell reflection

